{"tid":1657274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[預言] 沙中線單嘢，最後一定無事","createTime":"2019-10-16T04:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T04:27:17.000Z","uid":83648,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"376711018de7587ae6bc3625bb6cf11dc746a8be","tid":1657274,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"黨鐵突然咁幫政府唔會係無條件<br />\n佢哋一定知個後果係畀一部分市民放棄<br />\n<br />\n而近嚟黨鐵又有咩痛腳可以畀政府捉住撚呢？<br />\n無錯就係沙中綫<br />\n政府一定知道黨鐵啲衰嘢<br />\n而又幫手圍威喂<br />\n到咗呢啲時候就係收黨鐵頭嘅時候<br />\n沙中線單嘢隨時有骨牌效應<br />\n一陣政府爆埋其他嘢出嚟就仆硬街<br />\n<br />\n況且仲起碼有一半市民會搭鐵<br />\n賣樓又一定會大賣<br />\n<br />\n所以沙中綫呢個deal係值得做"},{"pid":"af07e926bce3e5a7febf5eb9ce2a7c32e4216f16","tid":1657274,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d5d4178cb09e3e2bfe7be1ca5e2d6e9b31f6edbb","tid":1657274,"uid":158235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"政府本身已經係大股東啦"},{"pid":"e981339f1cc9603a3be146640c45932e5e173073","tid":1657274,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"唔止沙中線 <br />\n<br />\n乜鳩線 <br />\n<br />\n都冇事 <br />\n<br />\n重話遲啲買大陸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔想搭搭下車 死了<br />\nEmpty R, no thx"}]}